Sounds like a short circuit in the 9 terminal flasher relay which
works both the turn signals and emegency flashers, pretty common for
this old of said relay.  Probably a bad diode or two.  If you're 12
volt, time to consider an upgrade to a conversion relay system
available for many years:

http://www.airheadparts.com/vintage-vw-parts/flasher-emergency-relay/flasher-
emergency-relay-repro-12v-211953227-b
